<%- layout("layouts/boilerplate") %>

<div class="host-home-page">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="hero-section">
      <h1>Your home could make money on Wanderlust</h1>
      <p class="lead">Join over 5 million hosts from around the world</p>
      <p>It's easy to get started and now you can find a co-host to do the hosting for you.</p>
      <div class="cta-buttons">
        <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Get started</a>
        <a href="#" class="btn btn-outline-primary btn-lg">Learn more</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-8">
        <h2>When you host, you're protected</h2>
        <p>AirCover for Hosts provides top-to-bottom protection for your home.</p>
        <div class="protection-features">
          <div class="feature-card">
            <h3><i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i> $1M damage protection</h3>
            <p>Your home is protected against damages caused by guests.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card">
            <h3><i class="fas fa-home"></i> Host liability insurance</h3>
            <p>You're covered if you're found legally responsible for a guest getting hurt.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card">
            <h3><i class="fas fa-clipboard-check"></i> AirCover for stays</h3>
            <p>Guests get protection too, which helps them book with confidence.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <a href="/aircover-for-hosts" class="btn-link">Learn about AirCover →</a>

        <h2>Your place looks great on Wanderlust</h2>
        <p>Our tools help you create a stunning listing that attracts guests.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Professional photography tips</li>
          <li>Listing description guidance</li>
          <li>Pricing recommendations</li>
          <li>Calendar management tools</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="#" class="btn-link">Download the Wanderlust app →</a>

        <h2>Top questions</h2>
        <div class="faq-section">
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>Is my place right for Wanderlust?</h3>
            <p>Most types of homes can be great listings. Learn what makes a successful host.</p>
            <a href="#" class="btn-link">Learn more →</a>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>How does hosting work?</h3>
            <p>You set your price, house rules, and availability. We handle the bookings and payments.</p>
            <a href="/join-hosting-class" class="btn-link">Take a free hosting class →</a>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>How do I get started?</h3>
            <p>Create your listing in minutes with our step-by-step guide.</p>
            <a href="#" class="btn-link">Get started now →</a>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>How do I get my space ready?</h3>
            <p>Simple tips to prepare your home for guests and provide a great experience.</p>
            <a href="#" class="btn-link">Prepare your home →</a>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>How often do I have to host?</h3>
            <p>You control when and how you host. Set your own schedule and availability.</p>
            <a href="#" class="btn-link">Control your hosting →</a>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>How does Wanderlust protect hosts?</h3>
            <p>AirCover for Hosts provides comprehensive protection for your home.</p>
            <a href="/aircover-for-hosts" class="btn-link">Learn about protection →</a>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>Are there any hosting regulations?</h3>
            <p>Learn about local regulations and how to host legally in your area.</p>
            <a href="#" class="btn-link">Learn about regulations →</a>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>Learn more about fees</h3>
            <p>Understand our fee structure and how much you can earn.</p>
            <a href="#" class="btn-link">Learn about fees →</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="sidebar-card">
          <h3>Quick start</h3>
          <p>Ready to start hosting? Create your listing today.</p>
          <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary btn-block">Create listing</a>
        </div>

        <div class="sidebar-card mt-4">
          <h3>Need a co-host?</h3>
          <p>Find a co-host to handle day-to-day hosting tasks for you.</p>
          <a href="/find-cohost" class="btn btn-outline-primary btn-block">Find a co-host</a>
        </div>

        <div class="sidebar-card mt-4">
          <h3>Hosting resources</h3>
          <ul class="sidebar-links">
            <li><a href="/hosting-resources">Resource Center</a></li>
            <li><a href="/community-forum">Community forum</a></li>
            <li><a href="/hosting-responsibly">Hosting responsibly</a></li>
            <li><a href="/join-hosting-class">Free hosting class</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="sidebar-card mt-4">
          <h3>Ask a host</h3>
          <p>Get answers from experienced hosts in our community.</p>
          <a href="/community-forum" class="btn btn-outline-primary btn-block">Ask a host</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
